WEBVTT

1
00:00:15.950 --> 00:00:17.890
(Lee Jun Young)

2
00:00:23.030 --> 00:00:25.660
(Lee Ju Myoung)

3
00:00:31.670 --> 00:00:34.340
(Jeon Hye Jin. Jin Goo)

4
00:00:48.950 --> 00:00:51.920
(Reborn Rookie)

5
00:01:22.826 --> 00:01:25.677
<i>Code Blue. Neurosurgery. Code Blue.</i>

6
00:01:25.701 --> 00:01:30.582
<i>All available neurosurgery personnel
to the VIP ICU.</i>

7
00:01:30.606 --> 00:01:33.147
<i>Code Blue. Neurosurgery. Code Blue.</i>

8
00:01:33.171 --> 00:01:38.417
<i>All available neurosurgery personnel
to the VIP ICU.</i>

9
00:01:53.459 --> 00:01:55.130
Get the defib. now!

10
00:01:57.600 --> 00:01:59.152
Charge to 200.

11
00:01:59.769 --> 00:02:01.070
Clear!

12
00:02:02.438 --> 00:02:03.839
Charge to 200 again.

13
00:02:15.193 --> 00:02:18.663
<i>He's still alive.</i>

14
00:02:18.687 --> 00:02:20.265
Prep the ECMO. now.

15
00:02:20.289 --> 00:02:23.358
Page the transport team
and get CS down here.

16
00:02:23.382 --> 00:02:25.302
- All hands on deck. move.
- On it.

17
00:02:25.326 --> 00:02:27.729
- Right now.
- Yes. Doctor.

18
00:02:30.726 --> 00:02:32.882
Why are you giving up already? Do more!

19
00:02:32.906 --> 00:02:35.137
Do whatever you can!

20
00:02:35.771 --> 00:02:37.405
Show some respect for the dead.

21
00:02:37.429 --> 00:02:39.675
This doesn't concern you.

22
00:02:43.746 --> 00:02:45.736
Mom!

23
00:02:45.760 --> 00:02:47.983
Mom. are you okay?

24
00:02:55.691 --> 00:02:56.759
(Il Jun's Mom)

25
00:02:58.360 --> 00:03:00.155
(Il Jun's Dad)

26
00:03:02.292 --> 00:03:03.775
<i>The person you are trying to reach
is not answering...</i>

27
00:03:03.799 --> 00:03:06.168
You just won't stop. will you...

28
00:03:13.142 --> 00:03:14.576
Doctor.

29
00:03:15.259 --> 00:03:18.947
Yeah. I need a minute alone.

30
00:03:35.593 --> 00:03:37.742
What the hell are you doing?

31
00:03:37.766 --> 00:03:38.841
Jae Seong.

32
00:03:38.865 --> 00:03:40.982
Did Jae Gyeong tell you to finish him off?

33
00:03:41.006 --> 00:03:43.805
What did you people do to my father?

34
00:03:44.640 --> 00:03:46.762
I think she injected
him with sleeping pills.

35
00:03:46.786 --> 00:03:49.442
If I don't give him the antidote right now.
he's going to die.

36
00:03:49.466 --> 00:03:51.154
What are you talking about?

37
00:03:51.178 --> 00:03:53.081
Are you saying we can save him?

38
00:03:53.105 --> 00:03:55.550
I've got a faint heartbeat.

39
00:03:56.757 --> 00:03:59.855
We have to save him. no matter what.

40
00:04:03.626 --> 00:04:05.161
Are you sure?

41
00:04:05.185 --> 00:04:07.796
If you're messing with
me about my father...

42
00:04:13.693 --> 00:04:15.103
Dad.

43
00:04:15.993 --> 00:04:17.218
Mr. Kang.

44
00:04:17.242 --> 00:04:18.774
Dad.

45
00:04:25.193 --> 00:04:27.023
He's breathing.

46
00:04:27.047 --> 00:04:29.050
Dad's breathing.

47
00:04:31.362 --> 00:04:33.939
I've got a pulse. We got him back.

48
00:04:33.963 --> 00:04:35.934
Dad.

49
00:04:35.958 --> 00:04:37.140
It's me.

50
00:04:37.164 --> 00:04:39.602
Jae Seong. I'm here.

51
00:04:39.626 --> 00:04:44.580
I knew you wouldn't let it end this way.

52
00:04:44.604 --> 00:04:47.936
No way you'd let
that bitch Jae Gyeong take you down.

53
00:04:50.039 --> 00:04:51.484
(Il Jun's Mom)

54
00:04:54.643 --> 00:04:56.219
(Il Jun's Mom)

55
00:04:58.914 --> 00:05:01.916
Go play along with your wife.

56
00:05:03.185 --> 00:05:06.097
Make sure she believes Dad is dead.
Not a word about this.

57
00:05:06.121 --> 00:05:08.666
He passed away a short while ago.

58
00:05:08.690 --> 00:05:10.659
What exactly is your plan?

59
00:05:14.359 --> 00:05:15.864
It's time...

60
00:05:16.559 --> 00:05:19.267
I stepped up as the eldest son.

61
00:05:22.971 --> 00:05:26.245
(Unclaimed Body)

62
00:05:36.771 --> 00:05:38.208
<i>Dad. aren't you sad?</i>

63
00:05:38.232 --> 00:05:40.856
<i>Grandpa just died.</i>

64
00:05:42.626 --> 00:05:43.936
<i>Congrats. honey.</i>

65
00:05:43.960 --> 00:05:46.705
<i>You got everything you wanted.</i>

66
00:05:46.729 --> 00:05:50.483
<i>I just want the truth about how he died.</i>

67
00:05:51.400 --> 00:05:53.001
<i>Then I'll be punished.</i>

68
00:05:54.511 --> 00:05:56.481
<i>I'm the one who should be glaring.</i>

69
00:05:56.505 --> 00:05:59.441
<i>Being linked to you
has been nothing but bad luck.</i>

70
00:06:00.860 --> 00:06:02.654
<i>I swore on Dad's grave.</i>

71
00:06:02.678 --> 00:06:05.490
<i>From now on. my only sister is you.</i>

72
00:06:05.514 --> 00:06:06.525
Dad.

73
00:06:06.549 --> 00:06:09.818
<i>And I owe you years
of being a real brother.</i>

74
00:06:13.193 --> 00:06:14.689
Dad.

75
00:06:17.860 --> 00:06:19.170
Dad.

76
00:06:19.194 --> 00:06:20.839
Just hang in there a little longer.

77
00:06:20.863 --> 00:06:22.664
You're going to pull through.

78
00:06:29.626 --> 00:06:31.149
Not again...

79
00:06:31.173 --> 00:06:33.108
He's dead.

80
00:06:44.593 --> 00:06:46.087
Bang Geul.

81
00:06:47.127 --> 00:06:48.790
Bang Geul!

82
00:06:55.331 --> 00:06:57.375
We've got an injured person over here!

83
00:06:57.399 --> 00:06:59.044
Call an ambulance!

84
00:06:59.068 --> 00:07:01.146
Ambulance!

85
00:07:01.170 --> 00:07:03.505
You can stop running now.

86
00:07:04.993 --> 00:07:07.036
Bang Geul.

87
00:07:07.060 --> 00:07:10.455
Why are you being so loud?

88
00:07:10.479 --> 00:07:13.134
You're giving me a splitting headache.

89
00:07:15.227 --> 00:07:16.785
Bang Geul.

90
00:07:44.026 --> 00:07:45.432
{\an8}You're here.

91
00:07:45.456 --> 00:07:47.248
{\an8}Is everyone okay?

92
00:07:50.659 --> 00:07:51.829
What happened to your head?

93
00:07:51.853 --> 00:07:53.722
Shouldn't you go to the hospital?

94
00:07:53.746 --> 00:07:56.342
They said it's just a small cut. I'm fine.

95
00:07:56.366 --> 00:07:59.309
Honestly. I thought it was really bad.

96
00:07:59.333 --> 00:08:01.264
Isn't that right?

97
00:08:04.384 --> 00:08:07.203
A second ago you were running
with her in your arms

98
00:08:07.227 --> 00:08:09.136
like she was dying.

99
00:08:09.160 --> 00:08:11.942
Why are you standing
there like a statue now?

100
00:08:11.966 --> 00:08:13.218
Go to the ER.

101
00:08:13.242 --> 00:08:14.853
Get a CT. an MRI.

102
00:08:14.877 --> 00:08:16.221
Don't come crying later when it hurts.

103
00:08:16.245 --> 00:08:18.156
Don't make a big deal out of it.

104
00:08:18.180 --> 00:08:20.161
Stop holding up busy people.

105
00:08:20.185 --> 00:08:22.069
Thank you.

106
00:08:22.093 --> 00:08:24.285
- Thank you so much.
- Thank you.

107
00:08:25.521 --> 00:08:26.602
Hey.

108
00:08:26.626 --> 00:08:28.669
Why would you let
Secretary Jo get his hands on that?

109
00:08:28.693 --> 00:08:31.087
You really want Choiseong to go under?

110
00:08:31.111 --> 00:08:33.261
That's what I'm saying.

111
00:08:33.893 --> 00:08:39.077
For God's sake. just
tell me what you're up to.

112
00:08:39.101 --> 00:08:40.552
We need to have a chat. you and me.

113
00:08:40.576 --> 00:08:41.579
You want to talk to me?

114
00:08:41.603 --> 00:08:43.147
I've got something important
to talk to you about.

115
00:08:43.171 --> 00:08:46.155
But I need answers from him.

116
00:08:46.179 --> 00:08:48.272
I should be in on this.

117
00:08:57.671 --> 00:08:59.240
Hey. Jun Hyeon.

118
00:09:01.690 --> 00:09:03.443
Should I march up to
Jae Gyeong and tell her

119
00:09:03.467 --> 00:09:05.848
you're teaming up with
Taeha to screw her over?

120
00:09:06.996 --> 00:09:08.499
Or maybe...

121
00:09:10.326 --> 00:09:12.210
I bring this to Chairman Na?

122
00:09:12.234 --> 00:09:14.235
Where did you get that?

123
00:09:15.292 --> 00:09:16.375
I stole it.

124
00:09:16.399 --> 00:09:17.749
Right out of Chairman Na's house.

125
00:09:17.773 --> 00:09:20.051
That guy Na Byeong Mo is no joke.

126
00:09:20.075 --> 00:09:22.711
What were you thinking?

127
00:09:23.478 --> 00:09:24.555
<i>Open your eyes!</i>

128
00:09:24.579 --> 00:09:25.735
<i>Wake up. Bang Geul!</i>

129
00:09:25.759 --> 00:09:27.248
<i>Can't you hear Dad?</i>

130
00:09:29.349 --> 00:09:31.564
Why do you care so much?

131
00:09:31.588 --> 00:09:32.298
What?

132
00:09:32.322 --> 00:09:34.533
You're worried about me.

133
00:09:34.557 --> 00:09:37.091
Everything you've been doing
was to keep me safe.

134
00:09:39.161 --> 00:09:41.172
She's my sister. He was my dad.

135
00:09:41.196 --> 00:09:42.366
The revenge is mine to take.

136
00:09:42.390 --> 00:09:44.246
Who are you to be jumping in?

137
00:09:44.270 --> 00:09:45.945
Why are you telling me to stay out of it?

138
00:09:45.969 --> 00:09:47.112
Who do you think you are?

139
00:09:47.136 --> 00:09:48.379
Yes.

140
00:09:48.403 --> 00:09:52.617
I'm losing sleep over you.
over your mom getting dragged into this.

141
00:09:52.641 --> 00:09:54.268
I'm worried sick

142
00:09:54.292 --> 00:09:57.378
you'll play avenger
and get caught by those bastards.

143
00:09:59.060 --> 00:10:00.548
"Those bastards"?

144
00:10:02.184 --> 00:10:05.630
Chairman Na was involved in killing my dad?

145
00:10:05.654 --> 00:10:08.700
Don't tell me he was
Jae Gyeong's accomplice.

146
00:10:08.724 --> 00:10:10.258
Hwang Jun Hyeon!

147
00:10:13.292 --> 00:10:15.673
I've been digging
into the security guard's phone

148
00:10:15.697 --> 00:10:17.565
trying to recover the hospital CCTV.

149
00:10:19.330 --> 00:10:24.278
They framed Jae Gyeong to grab Choiseong.

150
00:10:25.663 --> 00:10:27.776
Na Eun Se's the one who killed him.

151
00:10:34.793 --> 00:10:36.284
You sure?

152
00:10:44.169 --> 00:10:45.713
So my dad...

153
00:10:46.695 --> 00:10:51.800
was just a pawn the whole time?

154
00:10:59.093 --> 00:11:01.409
I'm really grateful for
everything you've done.

155
00:11:02.292 --> 00:11:03.945
But step back.

156
00:11:04.729 --> 00:11:06.514
This is my fight.

157
00:11:07.236 --> 00:11:08.693
They've killed people.

158
00:11:08.717 --> 00:11:11.272
You can't go after them by yourself!

159
00:11:11.296 --> 00:11:13.321
My heart just breaks for Dad.

160
00:11:14.186 --> 00:11:17.002
I need to show Dad he wasn't forgotten.

161
00:11:17.026 --> 00:11:21.673
I want him to know his life...

162
00:11:21.697 --> 00:11:23.464
wasn't some lonely ending.

163
00:11:37.793 --> 00:11:39.314
Don't...

164
00:11:41.693 --> 00:11:45.987
let this make you ugly. Bang Geul.

165
00:11:49.358 --> 00:11:54.629
Once your hands are dirty. once
you turn cold. revenge ends up...

166
00:11:56.659 --> 00:11:58.800
wrecking you.

167
00:12:00.526 --> 00:12:03.181
I don't want that for you.

168
00:12:03.205 --> 00:12:05.142
I'll handle the dirty work.

169
00:12:09.093 --> 00:12:11.722
I said this is my fight.

170
00:12:11.746 --> 00:12:14.983
- Why would you...
- Because your dad wouldn't want it.

171
00:12:18.396 --> 00:12:21.990
No dad in the world
wants his daughter to go down

172
00:12:24.926 --> 00:12:26.895
because of him.

173
00:12:39.860 --> 00:12:42.072
Come clean.

174
00:12:42.096 --> 00:12:44.539
You're hiding a daughter. aren't you?

175
00:12:47.927 --> 00:12:50.618
I'm letting you in.

176
00:12:52.659 --> 00:12:54.856
From now on. we do this together.

177
00:12:56.267 --> 00:12:57.659
Okay.

178
00:13:00.795 --> 00:13:03.941
(Chairman Na Byeong Mo)

179
00:13:03.965 --> 00:13:07.135
First. let's take down Secretary Jo.

180
00:13:20.009 --> 00:13:25.086
You want to... explain what happened today?

181
00:13:31.326 --> 00:13:33.805
Before that. you should
get a new secretary.

182
00:13:33.829 --> 00:13:36.942
How long are you going
to keep this thug by your side?

183
00:13:36.966 --> 00:13:39.734
You're a chairman of a
major conglomerate now.

184
00:13:40.817 --> 00:13:44.235
Thanks to him. I look like I
can't even finish off Bang Geul.

185
00:13:44.259 --> 00:13:45.740
But...

186
00:13:46.908 --> 00:13:50.088
He nearly ruined
the whole thing just to take credit.

187
00:13:50.112 --> 00:13:53.915
Plenty of smart guys out there.
Why waste time on this clown?

188
00:13:53.939 --> 00:13:55.026
Hwang Jun Hyeon.

189
00:13:55.050 --> 00:13:56.551
Enough.

190
00:13:58.699 --> 00:14:01.884
Get this to Taeha Energy.
Have them check the tech.

191
00:14:01.908 --> 00:14:04.136
Results will tell us.

192
00:14:04.160 --> 00:14:08.129
Brains or fists. We'll see which I need.

193
00:14:16.892 --> 00:14:18.948
What if Jae Gyeong starts asking questions?

194
00:14:18.972 --> 00:14:20.284
There was an incident.

195
00:14:20.308 --> 00:14:24.212
She's aware her sister's been making noise.
I'll blame her for it.

196
00:14:25.352 --> 00:14:27.308
She makes a decent shield.

197
00:14:27.332 --> 00:14:30.695
She lost the very tech
she was about to sell.

198
00:14:30.719 --> 00:14:33.848
Her position is shaky.

199
00:14:40.259 --> 00:14:41.539
(Lee Sang Jae)
<i>Forensics complete.</i>

200
00:14:41.563 --> 00:14:44.632
<i>Original CCTV recovered.</i>

201
00:14:47.013 --> 00:14:49.303
This is going to be one to watch.

202
00:14:50.993 --> 00:14:53.007
Look forward to it. Chairman.

203
00:15:08.826 --> 00:15:11.592
What is she doing here this late?

204
00:15:14.430 --> 00:15:19.177
<i>They framed Jae Gyeong to grab Choiseong.</i>

205
00:15:19.201 --> 00:15:21.334
<i>Na Eun Se's the one who killed him.</i>

206
00:15:33.693 --> 00:15:35.292
Lost your mind?

207
00:15:35.316 --> 00:15:37.085
You asking for it?

208
00:15:45.760 --> 00:15:47.103
You okay?

209
00:15:47.127 --> 00:15:48.302
Have you lost your mind?

210
00:15:48.326 --> 00:15:49.708
She's the crazy one.

211
00:15:49.732 --> 00:15:51.132
Hey!

212
00:15:52.259 --> 00:15:53.845
What's with the look?

213
00:15:53.869 --> 00:15:55.737
Wishing you'd died?

214
00:15:55.761 --> 00:15:57.957
Take it up with Jae Gyeong.

215
00:15:57.981 --> 00:16:00.584
Don't come crying to me.

216
00:16:00.608 --> 00:16:02.510
You feel untouchable now?

217
00:16:04.447 --> 00:16:06.137
Like the world is yours?

218
00:16:06.161 --> 00:16:07.615
Bang Geul.

219
00:16:10.292 --> 00:16:12.497
I outrank you in this family.

220
00:16:12.521 --> 00:16:14.889
Watch your mouth.

221
00:16:16.959 --> 00:16:20.247
You want to see me push it? I'll show you.

222
00:16:20.271 --> 00:16:21.911
Stay tuned.

223
00:16:23.093 --> 00:16:24.599
Go ahead.

224
00:16:25.491 --> 00:16:28.269
Who are you to scare me?

225
00:16:30.773 --> 00:16:33.017
That's enough. Go inside.

226
00:16:33.041 --> 00:16:34.836
Get off me.

227
00:16:34.860 --> 00:16:36.702
Blood really is thicker than water. huh?

228
00:16:36.726 --> 00:16:39.069
Seriously...

229
00:16:39.093 --> 00:16:43.718
I'm done with the Kangs.

230
00:16:57.800 --> 00:17:00.444
Spitting image of her
father. More and more.

231
00:17:00.468 --> 00:17:01.868
Right?

232
00:17:03.292 --> 00:17:06.010
Hey. did that shake you up?

233
00:17:06.034 --> 00:17:08.120
Your head's hurt.
right? Is that what it is?

234
00:17:08.144 --> 00:17:10.912
- Forget it. let's get you to a hospital.
- Jae Seong.

235
00:17:18.618 --> 00:17:23.824
It was Na Eun Se... Taeha was behind it...

236
00:17:48.050 --> 00:17:50.235
<i>Don't trust that girl.</i>

237
00:17:50.259 --> 00:17:55.866
<i>Chairman Na never makes a losing trade.
so why hand her to someone like you?</i>

238
00:17:55.890 --> 00:18:00.595
<i>Come on. I said don't worry about Eun Se.</i>

239
00:18:03.793 --> 00:18:05.600
Stupid bastard.

240
00:18:06.693 --> 00:18:08.636
Moron.

241
00:18:12.093 --> 00:18:14.041
This is all your fault.

242
00:18:17.226 --> 00:18:21.048
None of this would've happened without you.

243
00:18:23.127 --> 00:18:25.386
You did this.

244
00:18:44.093 --> 00:18:45.649
Mom!

245
00:18:45.673 --> 00:18:48.548
Let go! I'm bringing him home right now.

246
00:18:48.572 --> 00:18:50.821
Mom. just calm down first.

247
00:18:50.845 --> 00:18:54.148
Can you imagine what he's going through?

248
00:18:54.912 --> 00:18:59.230
What kind of life will Yi Jun have
under that woman?

249
00:18:59.254 --> 00:19:00.832
Are they even human?

250
00:19:00.856 --> 00:19:05.161
How could they do this to your dad?

251
00:19:05.185 --> 00:19:06.888
I know. Mom.

252
00:19:06.912 --> 00:19:13.169
I want to kill them right now.
but I'm holding back for Dad.

253
00:19:13.193 --> 00:19:16.435
I'm going to make
those scumbags tear each other apart.

254
00:19:16.459 --> 00:19:18.306
We are not sinking to their level.

255
00:19:19.659 --> 00:19:21.736
Mom.

256
00:19:21.760 --> 00:19:23.611
How could they...

257
00:19:32.026 --> 00:19:34.255
We're all set. Chairman.

258
00:19:37.798 --> 00:19:41.302
I told you to lay low until you
take over as president of Trading.

259
00:19:41.326 --> 00:19:44.543
I have to file for divorce anyway
because of Yi Jun.

260
00:19:44.567 --> 00:19:48.380
Since it's happening. I refuse to
spend another day in that house.

261
00:19:48.404 --> 00:19:50.301
It's not a good look.

262
00:19:50.325 --> 00:19:52.793
Why does that matter?

263
00:19:52.817 --> 00:19:55.242
We have Jae Gyeong right where we want her.

264
00:19:59.347 --> 00:20:00.741
(Managing Director Kwon)

265
00:20:01.426 --> 00:20:03.050
Yes. MD Kwon.

266
00:20:06.893 --> 00:20:09.156
Wait. what are you talking about?

267
00:20:11.359 --> 00:20:13.030
(Chairman Kang Jae Gyeong)

268
00:20:15.160 --> 00:20:16.831
You're firing me?

269
00:20:17.526 --> 00:20:18.805
On whose authority?

270
00:20:18.829 --> 00:20:22.285
Hiring and firing is a perk
of being the chairman.

271
00:20:22.309 --> 00:20:26.517
You think your position is safe
if you kick me out?

272
00:20:26.541 --> 00:20:28.309
I'm shaking.

273
00:20:29.009 --> 00:20:32.546
Are you really going to take me down?

274
00:20:37.326 --> 00:20:39.086
You're going to regret this.

275
00:20:50.721 --> 00:20:52.617
Aren't you pushing her a little too hard?

276
00:20:52.641 --> 00:20:55.280
She needs to be provoked to show her hand.

277
00:20:55.304 --> 00:20:57.569
I made that call because I trust you.

278
00:20:59.974 --> 00:21:01.936
You said you found
the hospital security footage.

279
00:21:01.960 --> 00:21:06.180
I searched the dead security guard's house
and found his phone.

280
00:21:09.326 --> 00:21:11.385
Here's the recovered footage.

281
00:21:16.426 --> 00:21:20.205
I wonder just how far
Eun Se is willing to go.

282
00:21:20.229 --> 00:21:22.635
Are you just going to let her
get away with this?

283
00:21:22.659 --> 00:21:24.302
Let's leak the security footage
and the recording

284
00:21:24.326 --> 00:21:25.976
and destroy Choiseong. Dad.

285
00:21:26.000 --> 00:21:28.898
<i>Don't do anything rash and just wait.</i>

286
00:21:28.922 --> 00:21:31.205
How much longer!

287
00:21:39.480 --> 00:21:40.872
(CEO Jeong Hak Hui. Hayoung Daily)

288
00:21:45.060 --> 00:21:49.701
CEO Jeong. go ahead and publish that tip.

289
00:21:49.725 --> 00:21:51.969
(Late Chairman Kang's Death: Footage Leaked)

290
00:21:51.993 --> 00:21:53.070
(Shocking Footage of Chairman Kang's Death)

291
00:21:53.094 --> 00:21:54.635
(The Truth Behind Chairman Kang's Death)

292
00:21:54.659 --> 00:21:57.569
{\an8}<i>At first.
she tried to inject the sleeping pills</i>

293
00:21:57.593 --> 00:22:00.550
{\an8}<i>she got from her husband
so Dad wouldn't wake up.</i>

294
00:22:00.574 --> 00:22:06.150
{\an8}<i>But when he suddenly opened his eyes.
she just smothered him with a pillow.</i>

295
00:22:06.174 --> 00:22:08.386
{\an8}<i>Your husband is an accomplice. too.</i>

296
00:22:08.410 --> 00:22:10.954
{\an8}<i>Do you really want to argue
over whose crime is worse?</i>

297
00:22:10.978 --> 00:22:12.056
(If he's an accomplice. they did it together)

298
00:22:12.080 --> 00:22:14.024
(Life in prison is too good for them)

299
00:22:14.048 --> 00:22:15.192
(Views)

300
00:22:15.216 --> 00:22:16.560
{\an8}(The released transcript may be
the only key evidence revealing the crime)

301
00:22:16.584 --> 00:22:22.527
{\an8}(Suspicious Death: 
Who Was the Last Visitor?)

302
00:22:23.893 --> 00:22:27.194
I told her to wait.
but she still went and pulled this stunt?

303
00:22:33.392 --> 00:22:34.569
Chairman.

304
00:22:34.593 --> 00:22:37.973
there's an issue with the hydrogen
tech files we took from Choiseong.

305
00:22:37.997 --> 00:22:39.516
We checked them several times.

306
00:22:39.540 --> 00:22:42.810
but they're an older version
than what we already had.

307
00:22:46.392 --> 00:22:48.582
<i>This is going to be one to watch.</i>

308
00:22:49.358 --> 00:22:51.521
<i>Look forward to it. Chairman.</i>

309
00:22:51.545 --> 00:22:54.154
Hwang Jun Hyeon. that bastard.

310
00:23:06.392 --> 00:23:10.849
{\an8}(Choiseong Press Briefing)
I deeply apologize for the shock

311
00:23:10.873 --> 00:23:14.021
and disappointment
many of you must have felt.

312
00:23:15.863 --> 00:23:18.235
After much agonizing.

313
00:23:18.259 --> 00:23:21.448
I am standing here today because I decided

314
00:23:22.950 --> 00:23:25.119
I can no longer hide the truth.

315
00:23:26.589 --> 00:23:31.025
The truth is. I am being blackmailed

316
00:23:33.763 --> 00:23:36.497
over my father's death.

317
00:23:38.626 --> 00:23:40.910
Is it true you visited
his hospital room that day?

318
00:23:40.934 --> 00:23:43.046
Are you also denying
the contents of the recording?

319
00:23:43.070 --> 00:23:46.069
We suspect the person
demanding a huge sum of money

320
00:23:46.093 --> 00:23:48.852
with the fabricated recording and footage

321
00:23:48.876 --> 00:23:53.502
is the same individual

322
00:23:53.526 --> 00:23:57.318
who broke
into the Daesan Hydrogen Complex recently

323
00:23:58.117 --> 00:24:00.534
and leaked our core hydrogen tech.

324
00:24:00.558 --> 00:24:02.494
Have you identified a suspect?

325
00:24:02.518 --> 00:24:06.570
We handed their identity over to the police
along with the security footage as evidence.

326
00:24:06.594 --> 00:24:09.139
We also believe
the real culprit who killed my father

327
00:24:09.163 --> 00:24:11.154
is part of the same group.

328
00:24:11.178 --> 00:24:14.635
Are you saying the late Chairman
Kang Yong Ho was murdered?

329
00:24:17.860 --> 00:24:20.841
We've secured evidence
pointing to the real culprit.

330
00:24:28.115 --> 00:24:29.229
(Choiseong Press Briefing)

331
00:24:30.026 --> 00:24:31.936
What is that?

332
00:24:31.960 --> 00:24:33.821
Isn't that Chairman Kang?

333
00:24:43.993 --> 00:24:48.635
Did the culprit dress up as you
to kill your father?

334
00:24:48.659 --> 00:24:49.824
Do you also have the original footage?

335
00:24:49.848 --> 00:24:51.622
You used the word "group."

336
00:24:51.646 --> 00:24:53.235
Are you saying they didn't act alone?

337
00:24:53.259 --> 00:24:54.635
Can you identify them?

338
00:24:54.659 --> 00:24:56.069
Is it someone from inside Choiseong?

339
00:24:56.093 --> 00:24:58.169
Why are you just now releasing the footage?

340
00:24:58.193 --> 00:24:59.747
I ask that...

341
00:25:03.559 --> 00:25:06.053
you stop exploiting...

342
00:25:06.926 --> 00:25:09.602
my father's death...

343
00:25:09.626 --> 00:25:15.262
so he can... finally rest in peace.

344
00:25:24.292 --> 00:25:27.041
Her acting is seriously
giving me the creeps.

345
00:25:33.883 --> 00:25:38.585
She's just using my dad
right up to the very end.

346
00:25:50.459 --> 00:25:52.109
Public opinion has completely flipped.

347
00:25:52.133 --> 00:25:54.446
There are wild guesses flying around
about the real culprit.

348
00:25:54.470 --> 00:25:57.981
Since your daughter is also implicated
in the recording.

349
00:25:58.005 --> 00:26:01.041
the focus might shift to Taeha
if we're not careful.

350
00:26:02.760 --> 00:26:04.454
What do we do. Dad?

351
00:26:04.478 --> 00:26:08.615
When you swing a sword recklessly.
you're bound to cut yourself.

352
00:26:10.426 --> 00:26:13.063
How does Jae Gyeong
have the original footage?

353
00:26:13.087 --> 00:26:14.787
You said you took care of everything.

354
00:26:14.811 --> 00:26:17.169
You blaming your own father now?

355
00:26:17.193 --> 00:26:21.169
You forced me in there
because you got sick of waiting around

356
00:26:21.193 --> 00:26:23.564
for somebody else to bring you Choiseong.

357
00:26:24.410 --> 00:26:26.486
You wanted me to be
the one to finish him off.

358
00:26:26.510 --> 00:26:27.512
So?

359
00:26:27.536 --> 00:26:32.406
Nobody was happier than you
when Chairman Kang died.

360
00:26:35.756 --> 00:26:40.314
so I don't deserve any of this.

361
00:26:42.160 --> 00:26:44.569
- Hey. stop them!
- Who are you people?

362
00:26:44.593 --> 00:26:46.196
Who are you people?

363
00:26:46.220 --> 00:26:47.253
Jo Taek Sang.

364
00:26:47.277 --> 00:26:49.802
you're under arrest for trespassing
and industrial espionage.

365
00:26:49.826 --> 00:26:51.313
You have the right to an attorney.

366
00:26:51.337 --> 00:26:55.435
You have the right to remain silent. and
anything you say can be used against you.

367
00:26:55.459 --> 00:26:59.669
Heads up.
You. your chairman. and the executives

368
00:26:59.693 --> 00:27:02.703
could all be brought
in over that stolen tech.

369
00:27:06.893 --> 00:27:08.942
Dad.

370
00:27:12.847 --> 00:27:15.654
(Kang Jae Gyeong)

371
00:27:33.932 --> 00:27:35.469
This way.

372
00:27:40.026 --> 00:27:41.842
Brains always win. don't they?

373
00:27:42.693 --> 00:27:45.490
Looks like you need a new secretary.

374
00:27:45.514 --> 00:27:48.949
Good luck finding talent like mine.

375
00:27:49.585 --> 00:27:52.796
Remember that security guard you killed?

376
00:27:52.820 --> 00:27:55.233
Mr. Hwang found his phone.

377
00:27:55.257 --> 00:27:57.502
Found some pretty interesting stuff on it.

378
00:27:57.526 --> 00:28:00.994
Should've killed that bastard too.

379
00:28:04.018 --> 00:28:07.515
Thanks to you. I had
the best laugh in ages.

380
00:28:08.193 --> 00:28:10.382
Really something. aren't you?

381
00:28:10.406 --> 00:28:14.418
You made your daughter do the killing.

382
00:28:14.442 --> 00:28:17.511
I'm actually starting to feel bad for her.

383
00:28:18.493 --> 00:28:22.869
By the way. once people find out...

384
00:28:22.893 --> 00:28:28.903
you murdered your in-law for Choiseong.
Taeha's done. right?

385
00:28:32.031 --> 00:28:34.261
I've got a soft heart.

386
00:28:35.430 --> 00:28:38.176
Hand over Taeha Energy.

387
00:28:38.200 --> 00:28:40.746
You nearly framed me
as the beast who murdered Dad.

388
00:28:40.770 --> 00:28:44.502
That much is the bare minimum
if you want my help.

389
00:28:44.526 --> 00:28:45.802
And...

390
00:28:45.826 --> 00:28:48.985
The money for the buyout?

391
00:28:49.009 --> 00:28:51.378
That's on you. right?

392
00:28:53.926 --> 00:28:58.652
You've got a stash
tucked away in Singapore.

393
00:29:16.481 --> 00:29:20.069
Mr. Hwang dug that up too.

394
00:29:20.093 --> 00:29:22.476
He scares even me sometimes.

395
00:29:26.060 --> 00:29:28.115
A lot to think about. isn't it?

396
00:29:29.083 --> 00:29:32.896
Cutting your daughter loose
won't make this go away.

397
00:29:32.920 --> 00:29:35.198
- Watch your mouth.
- Keep your voice down.

398
00:29:35.222 --> 00:29:36.790
Dad.

399
00:29:43.960 --> 00:29:49.910
I'll think about it
if you bury Kang Yong Ho's death for good.

400
00:29:52.049 --> 00:29:54.741
The living have to keep living.

401
00:29:55.883 --> 00:30:01.871
I'm not cruel enough
to cut off your people's livelihood.

402
00:30:16.826 --> 00:30:20.176
How did you find out about this?

403
00:30:20.200 --> 00:30:24.916
You asked Chairman Kang about
overseas tax havens before. didn't you?

404
00:30:24.940 --> 00:30:27.651
Even though he called you pathetic

405
00:30:27.675 --> 00:30:31.922
for cheaply copying
everything a chaebol chairman does.

406
00:30:31.946 --> 00:30:33.923
How do you know that?

407
00:30:33.947 --> 00:30:38.085
Since you were family.
he couldn't just ignore you.

408
00:30:39.655 --> 00:30:43.166
He showed you how.
but kept copies of all the documents.

409
00:30:43.190 --> 00:30:45.101
(Taeha Group Chairman Na Byeong Mo's
Slush Fund Records)

410
00:30:45.125 --> 00:30:47.470
Of course. even Chairman Kang never thought

411
00:30:47.494 --> 00:30:50.173
this card would be used
in a situation like this.

412
00:30:50.197 --> 00:30:52.208
Chairman Kang told you?

413
00:30:52.232 --> 00:30:53.308
Why?

414
00:30:53.332 --> 00:30:54.795
Who exactly are you?

415
00:30:54.819 --> 00:30:56.236
Good question.

416
00:30:57.726 --> 00:30:59.773
Who do you think I am?

417
00:31:01.944 --> 00:31:06.747
Please get ready
for Singapore as soon as possible.

418
00:31:15.055 --> 00:31:18.559
(Chairman Kang Jae Gyeong)

419
00:31:22.200 --> 00:31:27.134
Thanks to you.
I kept my seat and got Taeha Energy.

420
00:31:28.135 --> 00:31:32.551
I pulled off what my father couldn't.

421
00:31:32.575 --> 00:31:35.657
What would I ever do without you?

422
00:31:38.493 --> 00:31:42.749
<i>Should we just swallow Taeha whole?</i>

423
00:31:43.953 --> 00:31:45.919
Not on my watch.

424
00:31:52.254 --> 00:31:54.169
Where have you been this late?

425
00:31:54.193 --> 00:31:57.809
Just... went for a walk.

426
00:31:57.833 --> 00:31:59.734
It's dangerous out there...

427
00:32:04.678 --> 00:32:06.759
It'll be over soon.

428
00:32:07.846 --> 00:32:10.310
Kang Jae Gyeong and Taeha.

429
00:32:13.213 --> 00:32:14.613
Well...

430
00:32:15.559 --> 00:32:17.469
About Seok Do...

431
00:32:17.493 --> 00:32:18.885
What?

432
00:32:21.943 --> 00:32:23.623
Never mind.

433
00:32:24.593 --> 00:32:26.827
You're going on a business trip tomorrow?

434
00:32:42.172 --> 00:32:43.936
You came alone?

435
00:32:43.960 --> 00:32:45.288
You've got some nerve.

436
00:32:45.312 --> 00:32:49.716
She said she won't let it slide
if I get a single scratch.

437
00:32:51.693 --> 00:32:54.754
Do whatever you want
if you want to make the 9 o'clock news.

438
00:32:56.093 --> 00:32:57.400
Oh. I'm terrified.

439
00:32:57.424 --> 00:32:58.603
Economy?

440
00:32:58.627 --> 00:33:01.515
You should spend a little money
for an important trip like this.

441
00:33:01.539 --> 00:33:02.874
I'm in first class.

442
00:33:02.898 --> 00:33:04.323
First.

443
00:33:06.533 --> 00:33:08.401
That little...

444
00:33:12.493 --> 00:33:15.455
Yes. Chairman. I'm boarding now.

445
00:33:15.479 --> 00:33:17.975
Did you get the money launderers?

446
00:33:17.999 --> 00:33:20.356
<i>The guys who helped you set up Siren.</i>

447
00:33:20.380 --> 00:33:23.116
I arranged for you to
meet them in Singapore.

448
00:33:24.442 --> 00:33:25.635
What about the shell company

449
00:33:25.659 --> 00:33:28.139
to use as a cushion
for Na Byeong Mo's money laundering?

450
00:33:28.163 --> 00:33:31.067
I have an expert for that. so don't worry.

451
00:33:31.091 --> 00:33:32.637
<i>I'm not worried.</i>

452
00:33:32.661 --> 00:33:34.260
<i>Keep up the good work.</i>

453
00:33:36.326 --> 00:33:38.064
Careful there.

454
00:33:39.826 --> 00:33:41.334
Thank you.

455
00:33:46.793 --> 00:33:50.644
Why is she dressed like that again?

456
00:33:53.426 --> 00:33:55.448
Everyone's staring.

457
00:33:56.850 --> 00:33:58.730
(Taeha Energy Business
and Operations Analysis)

458
00:34:06.593 --> 00:34:10.383
Let's wrap up the Taeha Energy M&A plan
before Team Leader Hwang gets back.

459
00:34:10.407 --> 00:34:12.265
- Yes. Chairman.
- Yes. Chairman.

460
00:34:13.967 --> 00:34:15.368
What about my husband?

461
00:34:16.392 --> 00:34:18.338
What's he been up to lately?

462
00:34:35.991 --> 00:34:38.743
You always blew me off saying you were
busy.

463
00:34:38.767 --> 00:34:41.261
but you're sure playing a lot of golf.

464
00:34:42.593 --> 00:34:45.999
I haven't played in a while.
so my body feels stiff.

465
00:34:46.733 --> 00:34:48.604
Plus. you've been busy.

466
00:34:50.526 --> 00:34:52.851
You've changed a bit.

467
00:34:52.875 --> 00:34:54.679
Your whole vibe. too.

468
00:34:55.893 --> 00:34:57.938
We went through a lot.

469
00:34:57.962 --> 00:35:00.113
Anyone would change after that.

470
00:35:10.826 --> 00:35:14.961
Do you like... the new car?

471
00:35:37.618 --> 00:35:40.018
(Therapeutic Strategies
for Recovery in Hypoxic Brain Injury)

472
00:35:51.795 --> 00:35:55.277
Are you doing volunteer
work... out of guilt?

473
00:35:55.301 --> 00:35:56.902
Or...

474
00:35:56.926 --> 00:35:59.506
are you trying to resurrect
my cremated father?

475
00:36:14.392 --> 00:36:17.136
What would people say
if a guy who only saw patients

476
00:36:17.160 --> 00:36:19.104
suddenly jumped into corporate work?

477
00:36:19.128 --> 00:36:21.833
You want them calling
me your nepotism hire?

478
00:36:21.857 --> 00:36:24.558
I don't want to be your puppet
in Chemicals or Trading.

479
00:36:24.582 --> 00:36:27.952
I'm thinking of starting
a medical business division for neurology.

480
00:36:27.976 --> 00:36:31.805
Treating your father
got me interested in coma cases.

481
00:36:36.576 --> 00:36:41.314
You quit the hospital. yet you took
syringes and coma meds with you.

482
00:36:42.336 --> 00:36:47.013
I just thought...
you were up to something shady.

483
00:36:47.037 --> 00:36:48.521
Jae Gyeong.

484
00:36:50.199 --> 00:36:51.725
Are you scared?

485
00:36:52.507 --> 00:36:54.761
Scared that I'll leave you. too?

486
00:36:56.559 --> 00:36:58.443
Leave?

487
00:36:58.467 --> 00:37:00.583
I was the one who threw them away.

488
00:37:00.607 --> 00:37:05.302
I ended that toxic relationship
they called family.

489
00:37:05.326 --> 00:37:08.208
I only need you and Il Jun.

490
00:37:11.647 --> 00:37:15.548
I'll tell them to push forward
with the medical division.

491
00:37:17.227 --> 00:37:19.352
I'm the chairman of Choiseong.

492
00:37:20.102 --> 00:37:22.389
You have nothing to be ashamed of.

493
00:37:31.227 --> 00:37:33.867
- To the office.
- Yes. ma'am.

494
00:37:34.601 --> 00:37:36.778
I have a lot of TF team work.

495
00:37:36.802 --> 00:37:38.492
You're heading home. right?

496
00:38:18.814 --> 00:38:22.515
Sir. you absolutely cannot lose that car.

497
00:38:51.794 --> 00:38:53.446
Mrs. Jo.

498
00:38:58.854 --> 00:39:01.421
Hold on! Please listen to me first!

499
00:39:05.060 --> 00:39:06.593
Wait!

500
00:39:14.326 --> 00:39:16.469
How did you find this place?

501
00:39:40.096 --> 00:39:46.023
You've been doing this... behind my back?

502
00:39:46.833 --> 00:39:48.547
I'm sorry.

503
00:39:48.571 --> 00:39:50.435
I was terrified...

504
00:39:50.459 --> 00:39:54.786
he might take a turn for the worse
and hurt you even more.

505
00:39:54.810 --> 00:39:59.889
I was just too scared... to tell you.

506
00:39:59.913 --> 00:40:01.814
I have no excuses.

507
00:40:08.691 --> 00:40:10.823
Thank you. Jae Seong.

508
00:40:14.359 --> 00:40:18.364
Thank you... for saving him.

509
00:40:20.738 --> 00:40:23.848
Thank you for letting me see him again.

510
00:40:27.910 --> 00:40:30.455
I'm so grateful.

511
00:40:30.479 --> 00:40:32.084
I'll make sure...

512
00:40:32.693 --> 00:40:37.317
he wakes up. Mother.

513
00:40:46.393 --> 00:40:49.628
Is he really handing that slush fund
over to Kang Jae Gyeong?

514
00:40:49.652 --> 00:40:51.364
Not a chance.

515
00:40:52.251 --> 00:40:54.513
This is Na Byeong Mo's slush fund file.

516
00:40:54.537 --> 00:40:58.784
It has everything
from his Singapore accounts to his proxies.

517
00:40:58.808 --> 00:41:02.702
Jun Hyeon left it for us
to hand over to the police.

518
00:41:02.726 --> 00:41:06.702
Then why did they take Na Eun Se
all the way to Singapore?

519
00:41:06.726 --> 00:41:08.994
Bang Geul said it herself.

520
00:41:09.018 --> 00:41:10.826
"Manager.

521
00:41:10.850 --> 00:41:12.936
how solid do you think
a father-daughter bond is

522
00:41:12.960 --> 00:41:14.973
when they've committed murder?"

523
00:41:14.997 --> 00:41:18.236
Na Byeong Mo won't even consider
saving his daughter.

524
00:41:18.260 --> 00:41:20.514
He's only worried about
the group taking a hit.

525
00:41:20.538 --> 00:41:22.040
Bingo.

526
00:41:22.064 --> 00:41:23.906
She said that's what they're counting on.

527
00:41:23.930 --> 00:41:26.693
What are you two doing? Come on out.

528
00:41:26.717 --> 00:41:29.047
- Coming.
- Yes. ma'am.

529
00:41:29.071 --> 00:41:30.506
Right.

530
00:41:34.627 --> 00:41:37.587
We'll keep you safe
until your grandson gets back.

531
00:41:37.611 --> 00:41:39.991
Just think of us as your two new sons.

532
00:41:40.015 --> 00:41:41.615
Makes you feel safe. right?

533
00:41:42.318 --> 00:41:43.793
I cooked up some chicken.

534
00:41:43.817 --> 00:41:45.163
Have a seat.

535
00:41:45.187 --> 00:41:47.121
Oh. really?

536
00:41:47.145 --> 00:41:48.130
Oh...

537
00:41:48.154 --> 00:41:51.958
I was actually just thinking
something smelled amazing.

538
00:41:52.768 --> 00:41:55.371
We're the ones
supposed to be taking care of you.

539
00:41:55.395 --> 00:41:58.741
I heard you help Jun Hyeon out a lot.

540
00:41:58.765 --> 00:42:01.811
The girl next door told me
you're his best friends.

541
00:42:01.835 --> 00:42:03.112
- Yes. ma'am.
- Yes. ma'am.

542
00:42:03.136 --> 00:42:04.213
You boys drink. right?

543
00:42:04.237 --> 00:42:06.965
- Thank you for the drinks.
- Stay seated.

544
00:42:06.989 --> 00:42:09.424
- I'll whip this up quickly.
- Sounds good.

545
00:42:09.448 --> 00:42:13.179
- It'll be right out.
- Looks like we're the ones being treated here.

546
00:42:15.348 --> 00:42:16.374
Are you crying again?

547
00:42:16.398 --> 00:42:18.634
Must be male menopause.

548
00:42:19.392 --> 00:42:22.208
Just wait till Jun Hyeon gets back.

549
00:42:22.232 --> 00:42:23.866
I'm going to treat him so well.

550
00:42:23.890 --> 00:42:25.525
Come on.

551
00:42:26.493 --> 00:42:28.240
Have a seat.

552
00:42:28.264 --> 00:42:32.608
(Singapore)

553
00:42:32.632 --> 00:42:35.981
Write Chairman Na's Singapore account here.

554
00:42:36.005 --> 00:42:39.205
Take seven percent.
Send the rest to this foundation account.

555
00:42:44.760 --> 00:42:46.869
A seven percent fee?

556
00:42:46.893 --> 00:42:48.936
So after taking a 35 billion won cut.

557
00:42:48.960 --> 00:42:53.419
Jae Gyeong is just pocketing
over 450 billion won.

558
00:42:55.726 --> 00:42:57.523
Just sign it.

559
00:42:58.625 --> 00:42:59.672
(JH Soccer Club)

560
00:42:59.696 --> 00:43:01.635
JH?

561
00:43:01.659 --> 00:43:03.896
As in Hwang Jun Hyeon's JH?

562
00:43:05.434 --> 00:43:09.124
You slapped this together for laundering.
then you'll shut it down. Right?

563
00:43:09.148 --> 00:43:12.011
An expert put a lot of thought into this.

564
00:43:12.035 --> 00:43:13.293
Who knows?

565
00:43:13.317 --> 00:43:15.393
It might actually become
a prestigious soccer foundation.

566
00:43:15.417 --> 00:43:17.936
Order some champagne.

567
00:43:17.960 --> 00:43:20.300
We have way too much
time before our flight.

568
00:43:20.324 --> 00:43:22.406
Let me walk you out.

569
00:43:23.235 --> 00:43:25.259
Excuse me.

570
00:43:29.534 --> 00:43:34.068
You guys...
need to earn your plane tickets. right?

571
00:43:41.846 --> 00:43:43.723
(Kang Bang Geul)
<i>Let's begin.</i>

572
00:43:47.615 --> 00:43:48.724
(CEO Jeong. Hayoung Daily)

573
00:43:53.168 --> 00:43:55.665
It's me. Kang Jae Seong.

574
00:44:15.679 --> 00:44:18.377
Are you sure about this? Doing this to me?

575
00:44:18.401 --> 00:44:21.000
Stop acting up
just because you trust Jae Gyeong.

576
00:44:21.024 --> 00:44:23.751
Guys like you are disposable
and a dime a dozen.

577
00:44:24.524 --> 00:44:26.721
Who says I trust Kang Jae Gyeong?

578
00:44:37.268 --> 00:44:39.913
The Daesan Hydrogen Complex
wasn't a coincidence. was it?

579
00:44:39.937 --> 00:44:42.164
You were just pretending to be on her side

580
00:44:42.188 --> 00:44:44.415
while working with Bang
Geul this whole time?

581
00:44:44.439 --> 00:44:46.774
Did you play all of us?

582
00:44:50.823 --> 00:44:53.648
Makes things easier
that you catch on so fast.

583
00:44:56.768 --> 00:44:58.805
He probably won't answer.

584
00:44:58.829 --> 00:45:01.289
Chairman Na is going
through hell right now.

585
00:45:02.801 --> 00:45:05.169
<i>Breaking news. The suspected murderer</i>

586
00:45:05.193 --> 00:45:07.204
{\an8}(Hospital CCTV Footage)
<i>of the late Chairman Kang of Choiseong Group</i>

587
00:45:07.228 --> 00:45:09.252
{\an8}<i>is believed to be his
daughter-in-law. Ms. Na.</i>

588
00:45:09.276 --> 00:45:11.031
{\an8}<i>sending shockwaves through the public.</i>

589
00:45:11.055 --> 00:45:14.222
{\an8}<i>With clear footage of
her face now released.</i>

590
00:45:14.246 --> 00:45:17.147
{\an8}<i>the fallout
surrounding the late Chairman Kang's death</i>

591
00:45:17.171 --> 00:45:20.184
<i>is expected to grow.</i>

592
00:45:20.208 --> 00:45:23.387
If you don't want to get arrested
like Secretary Jo.

593
00:45:23.411 --> 00:45:25.780
it's every man for himself from now on.

594
00:45:31.968 --> 00:45:34.155
Then did you guys take the slush fund. too?

595
00:45:35.901 --> 00:45:37.968
Is this why you brought me here
in the first place?

596
00:45:37.992 --> 00:45:39.837
To trap me in a foreign country?

597
00:45:39.861 --> 00:45:41.862
Hwang Jun Hyeon. you bastard!

598
00:45:44.031 --> 00:45:46.043
Instead of playing the victim.

599
00:45:46.067 --> 00:45:48.044
you should be on your knees
begging Bang Geul for forgiveness.

600
00:45:48.068 --> 00:45:51.105
admitting you're a monster
who committed a deadly sin.

601
00:45:52.740 --> 00:45:57.557
Do you even realize what you've done
just to catch the killer of a dead old man?

602
00:46:01.568 --> 00:46:04.085
You think my dad
will let you get away with this?

603
00:46:06.668 --> 00:46:09.156
You still trust your dad. huh?

604
00:46:10.086 --> 00:46:14.395
Will Chairman Na save you.
or will he save Taeha?

605
00:46:18.903 --> 00:46:20.223
(CEO Jeon Jin Hwan. Taeha Energy)

606
00:46:23.071 --> 00:46:24.936
(CEO Shin Yong Ha. Taeha Chemicals)

607
00:46:27.108 --> 00:46:28.569
(Eldest Son. Taeha Construction)

608
00:46:33.514 --> 00:46:35.116
(International Call)

609
00:46:39.268 --> 00:46:40.522
<i>Dad.</i>

610
00:46:40.546 --> 00:46:43.567
Eun Se. are you okay?

611
00:46:43.591 --> 00:46:45.827
(Suspect Believed
to Be Daughter-in-Law. Ms. Na)

612
00:46:46.601 --> 00:46:50.631
There's no way Mr. Hwang leaked the video
without consulting me first.

613
00:46:51.768 --> 00:46:54.068
What on earth is going on?

614
00:46:56.434 --> 00:46:57.905
Chairman.

615
00:47:23.631 --> 00:47:25.569
(Choiseong: The Future of New Business)

616
00:47:26.476 --> 00:47:29.111
That despicable monster!

617
00:47:31.110 --> 00:47:34.257
Eun Se is no longer a daughter of mine.

618
00:47:34.281 --> 00:47:37.096
I'll drag her in myself.
expose her crimes to the world.

619
00:47:37.120 --> 00:47:39.655
and make sure she gets what she deserves.

620
00:47:40.459 --> 00:47:43.138
You must have been through so much.

621
00:47:43.162 --> 00:47:46.141
Your father and I were old friends
before we became in-laws.

622
00:47:46.165 --> 00:47:49.210
I don't even know how to ask
the deceased for forgiveness.

623
00:47:49.234 --> 00:47:51.310
If failing to keep a
married daughter in line

624
00:47:51.334 --> 00:47:53.412
and being blind to all this
until it got to this point

625
00:47:53.436 --> 00:47:54.583
is a sin. then I am a sinner.

626
00:47:54.607 --> 00:47:58.741
Let me apologize... in her place.

627
00:48:10.277 --> 00:48:12.500
There are too many eyes here.

628
00:48:12.524 --> 00:48:14.857
Let's take this somewhere private.

629
00:48:16.994 --> 00:48:18.794
Chairman Na Byeong Mo.

630
00:48:20.299 --> 00:48:24.210
Your daughter. Na Eun Se.
left for Singapore yesterday. didn't she?

631
00:48:24.234 --> 00:48:26.152
I have no intention
of covering up my daughter's crimes.

632
00:48:26.176 --> 00:48:28.410
and I'll cooperate fully.

633
00:48:28.434 --> 00:48:29.771
As soon as she's back in Korea...

634
00:48:29.795 --> 00:48:33.955
Didn't you help her flee the country
to launder your slush fund?

635
00:48:33.979 --> 00:48:35.369
What?

636
00:48:37.213 --> 00:48:38.557
(Police for the People)
<i>Excuse me.</i>

637
00:48:38.581 --> 00:48:41.429
<i>where is the Anti-Corruption
and Economic Crime Investigation Unit?</i>

638
00:48:41.453 --> 00:48:43.278
<i>Just head this way.</i>

639
00:48:48.524 --> 00:48:51.038
(Taeha Group Chairman Na Byeong Mo's
Slush Fund Records)

640
00:48:51.897 --> 00:48:54.139
<i>Hot delivery coming through!</i>

641
00:48:54.163 --> 00:48:56.052
(Anti-Corruption
and Economic Crime Investigation Unit)

642
00:48:56.076 --> 00:48:57.585
Do you have any idea

643
00:48:57.609 --> 00:49:00.434
how many people try to drag me down
with false tips like that?

644
00:49:00.458 --> 00:49:03.494
Then you must know Ham Du Ho. right?

645
00:49:03.518 --> 00:49:05.287
He worked security
at Hangang University Hospital.

646
00:49:05.311 --> 00:49:07.312
and he died recently.

647
00:49:09.245 --> 00:49:10.835
Murdered. to be exact.

648
00:49:10.859 --> 00:49:14.630
And we have evidence
suggesting you ordered the hit.

649
00:49:14.654 --> 00:49:15.761
What a load of nonsense!

650
00:49:15.785 --> 00:49:18.554
<i>He contacted you too. right?</i>

651
00:49:19.245 --> 00:49:22.034
<i>There's another video
on the security guard's phone?</i>

652
00:49:22.058 --> 00:49:25.240
<i>Said he'd tell you the truth
if you paid enough.</i>

653
00:49:25.264 --> 00:49:28.241
<i>He got too greedy.</i>

654
00:49:28.265 --> 00:49:29.965
<i>Don't you think?</i>

655
00:49:30.970 --> 00:49:33.761
<i>Turns out he had
a hidden camera in his glasses.</i>

656
00:49:33.785 --> 00:49:37.619
<i>It recorded everything.
including Secretary Jo bribing him</i>

657
00:49:37.643 --> 00:49:39.186
<i>to steal the hospital CCTV footage.</i>

658
00:49:39.210 --> 00:49:43.792
<i>Let's show the world
who Na Byeong Mo really is.</i>

659
00:49:43.816 --> 00:49:45.481
<i>Sang Jae.</i>

660
00:49:46.843 --> 00:49:49.309
That's not my voice.

661
00:49:49.333 --> 00:49:52.409
Someone must have doctored it. just like
Chairman Kang Jae Gyeong's recording.

662
00:49:52.433 --> 00:49:55.170
My secretary acted on his own
out of some twisted loyalty.

663
00:49:55.194 --> 00:49:56.510
and now he's pinning it on me!

664
00:49:56.534 --> 00:49:59.952
We'll see about that
when we get you two in the same room.

665
00:49:59.976 --> 00:50:01.385
We've also put out a red notice.

666
00:50:01.409 --> 00:50:03.809
so you'll be reuniting
with your daughter very soon.

667
00:50:03.833 --> 00:50:05.219
I didn't know anything!

668
00:50:05.243 --> 00:50:07.110
I am innocent!

669
00:50:07.134 --> 00:50:09.919
Take your hands off me!

670
00:50:09.943 --> 00:50:11.774
Are you kidding me right now?

671
00:50:16.704 --> 00:50:20.092
<i>Following a surprise raid on Taeha Group.</i>

672
00:50:20.116 --> 00:50:23.729
<i>police are tracking down
the 300 billion won corporate loan</i>

673
00:50:23.753 --> 00:50:26.098
<i>Taeha took out to ostensibly acquire</i>

674
00:50:26.122 --> 00:50:28.166
<i>Choiseong Trading's hydrogen rights.</i>

675
00:50:28.190 --> 00:50:30.602
<i>which they stole without
paying the balance.</i>

676
00:50:30.626 --> 00:50:34.139
<i>Authorities also plan
to work closely with Singapore.</i>

677
00:50:34.163 --> 00:50:38.100
<i>where Chairman Na allegedly
hid his slush funds.</i>

678
00:50:40.403 --> 00:50:44.750
<i>Meanwhile. the whereabouts
of Na Eun Se. the prime suspect</i>

679
00:50:44.774 --> 00:50:47.386
<i>in the murder of late Choiseong
Chairman Kang. remain unknown.</i>

680
00:50:47.410 --> 00:50:50.789
<i>Chairman Na. currently under investigation.</i>

681
00:50:50.813 --> 00:50:54.459
<i>has reportedly stated that</i>

682
00:50:54.483 --> 00:50:56.452
<i>his daughter acted entirely on her own.</i>

683
00:50:56.476 --> 00:50:59.019
<i>Eun Se is no longer a daughter of mine.</i>

684
00:50:59.043 --> 00:51:01.867
<i>I'll drag her in myself.
expose her crimes to the world.</i>

685
00:51:01.891 --> 00:51:04.360
<i>and make sure she gets what she deserves.</i>

686
00:51:06.310 --> 00:51:07.752
<i>Eun Se.</i>

687
00:51:07.776 --> 00:51:09.086
<i>are you okay?</i>

688
00:51:09.110 --> 00:51:10.712
<i>We got completely played.</i>

689
00:51:10.736 --> 00:51:11.647
<i>Hwang Jun Hyeon. that bastard...</i>

690
00:51:11.671 --> 00:51:14.103
<i>Don't come back to Korea for a while.</i>

691
00:51:15.271 --> 00:51:16.281
<i>What?</i>

692
00:51:16.305 --> 00:51:20.752
<i>Go straight to Florida
and lay low at the villa.</i>

693
00:51:20.776 --> 00:51:21.888
<i>Dad...</i>

694
00:51:21.912 --> 00:51:24.626
<i>It's the best way to do damage control.</i>

695
00:51:24.650 --> 00:51:26.792
<i>Without hard evidence or a suspect.</i>

696
00:51:26.816 --> 00:51:28.994
<i>the investigation will just fizzle out.</i>

697
00:51:29.018 --> 00:51:31.485
<i>Just do as you're told for now.</i>

698
00:51:31.509 --> 00:51:33.501
<i>That's how we both survive.</i>

699
00:51:33.525 --> 00:51:35.968
<i>You hear me?</i>

700
00:51:35.992 --> 00:51:37.688
<i>Eun Se.</i>

701
00:51:37.712 --> 00:51:38.848
<i>Eun Se!</i>

702
00:51:38.872 --> 00:51:40.939
<i>Na Eun Se!</i>

703
00:51:40.963 --> 00:51:43.952
<i>He sounds desperate for a guy
selling out his own daughter.</i>

704
00:51:43.976 --> 00:51:45.152
<i>Shut up.</i>

705
00:51:45.176 --> 00:51:46.668
<i>Fine.</i>

706
00:51:46.692 --> 00:51:48.880
<i>Go ahead and play the martyr.</i>

707
00:51:48.904 --> 00:51:50.819
<i>Take the fall for him all by yourself.</i>

708
00:51:50.843 --> 00:51:52.975
<i>I said shut up!</i>

709
00:52:11.684 --> 00:52:15.534
It's either she goes down.
or she takes her father down.

710
00:52:15.558 --> 00:52:17.495
Must be quite the dilemma for her.

711
00:52:17.519 --> 00:52:19.335
She just watched him
throw her to the wolves.

712
00:52:19.359 --> 00:52:22.037
She's probably just figuring out
how to take him down.

713
00:52:31.542 --> 00:52:32.794
Yes. Chairman.

714
00:52:32.818 --> 00:52:34.986
Why are you so hard to reach?

715
00:52:35.010 --> 00:52:37.333
I just landed.

716
00:52:37.357 --> 00:52:39.113
I'll head straight back to the office.

717
00:52:39.137 --> 00:52:41.469
We have a lot to talk about.

718
00:52:41.493 --> 00:52:43.692
Alright.

719
00:52:48.143 --> 00:52:49.973
Can I get you something to eat?

720
00:52:49.997 --> 00:52:51.433
You haven't had dinner yet.

721
00:52:51.457 --> 00:52:53.599
I'm not hungry.

722
00:52:53.623 --> 00:52:55.593
You should head home too.

723
00:52:55.617 --> 00:52:57.952
And tell the task force to call it a day.

724
00:52:57.976 --> 00:52:59.408
Well...

725
00:53:09.844 --> 00:53:12.087
Did Jae Seong leave for the day?

726
00:53:35.776 --> 00:53:37.552
Call me if anything happens.

727
00:53:37.576 --> 00:53:39.394
Don't try to be a hero.

728
00:53:39.418 --> 00:53:41.393
Stop nagging and get going.

729
00:53:41.417 --> 00:53:43.958
Call me. no matter how late it is.

730
00:53:43.982 --> 00:53:45.454
Got it?

731
00:53:47.957 --> 00:53:50.292
Please drive safely.

732
00:53:51.322 --> 00:53:53.095
You promised. okay?

733
00:55:03.910 --> 00:55:06.756
Not enough evidence?

734
00:55:06.780 --> 00:55:09.636
Or just a killer legal team?

735
00:55:09.660 --> 00:55:12.320
Didn't expect you to be out this fast.

736
00:55:12.344 --> 00:55:15.576
I am the head
of a major conglomerate. after all.

737
00:55:15.600 --> 00:55:17.325
Though I admit. I was surprised myself.

738
00:55:17.349 --> 00:55:20.682
It's the first time
I've been stabbed in the back this hard.

739
00:55:26.910 --> 00:55:31.840
You stabbed your own daughter in the back
just to save your own neck.

740
00:55:31.864 --> 00:55:32.852
Cut the bullshit.

741
00:55:32.876 --> 00:55:34.529
What?

742
00:55:36.576 --> 00:55:39.735
That stench doesn't
wash off easily. does it?

743
00:55:40.836 --> 00:55:46.051
Doesn't matter how much designer
crap you wear or how fancy your chair is.

744
00:55:46.075 --> 00:55:48.420
Your filthy habits never change.

745
00:55:48.444 --> 00:55:50.045
You little bastard!

746
00:55:54.243 --> 00:55:59.511
That look in your eyes.
running your mouth with zero fear...

747
00:55:59.535 --> 00:56:02.124
you're exactly like him.

748
00:56:03.010 --> 00:56:05.193
Don't you recognize me?

749
00:56:06.219 --> 00:56:07.863
It's me.

750
00:56:08.743 --> 00:56:11.500
Kang Yong Ho. The man you murdered.

751
00:56:17.310 --> 00:56:22.081
You knew you couldn't beat me
unless you killed me!

752
00:56:22.105 --> 00:56:23.755
Aren't you ashamed?

753
00:56:23.779 --> 00:56:25.957
Causing all this chaos
just to plant a flag on my grave

754
00:56:25.981 --> 00:56:28.283
and pat yourself on the back?

755
00:56:30.176 --> 00:56:32.497
Glory is fleeting.
and it all ends when you die.

756
00:56:32.521 --> 00:56:34.169
What more could you possibly want?

757
00:56:34.193 --> 00:56:35.957
You little prick!

758
00:56:37.943 --> 00:56:41.206
You think I don't see right through you?

759
00:56:41.230 --> 00:56:45.304
Using naive Bang Geul to swallow up
Choiseong out of some petty revenge?

760
00:56:45.328 --> 00:56:46.678
I respect that.

761
00:56:46.702 --> 00:56:51.219
I like that kind of ambition.

762
00:56:51.243 --> 00:56:56.144
Too bad... you're not on my side.

763
00:57:06.110 --> 00:57:08.123
Say hi...

764
00:57:08.809 --> 00:57:10.826
to Kang Yong Ho for me.

765
00:57:45.542 --> 00:57:47.796
Why is he calling instead of coming up?

766
00:57:56.141 --> 00:57:58.611
(Dad)

767
00:58:06.982 --> 00:58:09.056
(Missed call: Dad)

768
00:58:21.643 --> 00:58:25.088
<i>You ruled the world
long enough. didn't you?</i>

769
00:58:25.112 --> 00:58:27.552
<i>How long are you going to block my path?</i>

770
00:58:27.576 --> 00:58:29.775
<i>What's still holding you here?</i>

771
00:58:29.799 --> 00:58:33.642
<i>Should I... end it for you?</i>

772
00:59:06.175 --> 00:59:10.611
(Chairman Kang Jae Gyeong)

773
00:59:30.336 --> 00:59:32.196
Dad...

774
00:59:48.442 --> 00:59:50.852
You should be thrilled.

775
00:59:51.523 --> 00:59:54.770
Daddy's back from the dead.
